  "title": "Sales Engineer (SCADA/PLC)",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>In charge of promoting and selling the company's products, integrated solutions, and services.</li><li>Responsible in working closely with the Business Development Manager in the preparation of tender bid submissions and proposals, including gathering functional and technical information and costing from in-house departments and/or from other vendors and OEM partners.</li><li>Responsible for pre-sales solution and proposal submission preparation for the assigned Request for Quote (RFQ) / Request for Proposal (RFP) from the clients, and promptly update the status to the relevant BD Manager</li><li>Actively in participating in sales presentations, maintain technical application and presentation materials </li><li>In charge of being involved and assist in the business division to explore new solutions/products to support the company’s business goals and to identify new business opportunities and expand our market share.</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Min Diploma in Electrical/ Electronics/ Computer, equivalent Engineering discipline.</li><li>Min 2 years of working experiences in any of these SCADA/PLC solutions, Building Management System, relevant Operation Technologies (OT/IOT) solution for Power, Water, Transportation industries are preferred. </li><li>Knowledge in OT network & cybersecurity solutions / Security & Surveillance solutions will be advantage.</li></ul><p>To submit your application, please apply online to <a href=\"mailto:apply@rn-care.com\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>apply@rn-care.com </strong></a>or call <strong>+(65) </strong><a href=\"tel:6513 5697\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><strong>6513 5697</strong></a> for private and confidential discussion.</p><p>Your interest will be treated with the strictest of confidence. We regret that only shortlisted candidates will be notified or contacted.</p><p><strong>RN Care Pte. Ltd</strong><br /><strong>EA License No: 17C8900</strong></p>",
